    "Jauhiainen et al. [2019] is a survey of automatic language identification.",
    "They describe that dialect detection may be more difficult than language detection since dialects may have lexical or syntactic overlap.",
    "In doing so, the survey does not make a distinction between languages and dialects -and treats different dialects as different class labels, while still maintaining a classification approach.",
    "However, one sees challenges in this regard.",
    "Boujou et al. [2021] present a baseline approach, which utilises classical machine learning."
  ],
